              selecting marker genes in scRNA-seq data. Our results highlight
              the efficacy of simple methods, especially the Wilcoxon rank-sum
              test, Student's t-test and logistic regression. All code used in
              the evaluation, including an extensible Snakemake pipeline, is
              available at:
              [https://gitlab.svi.edu.au/biocellgen-public/mage\_2020\_marker-gene-benchmarking][1].
              \#\#\# Competing Interest Statement The authors have declared no
